OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FA 66-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged over a car bomb attack
OL,8,Fon Dunmurry police station.
OL,10,FA hijacked delivery car exploded
OL,11,Foutside the station last Saturday
OL,12,Fnight as homes were being evacuated.
OL,14,FKieran Smyth, with an address at
OL,15,FBeechmount Avenue in Belfast, appeared
OL,16,Fbefore Lisburn Magistrates' Court on
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,19,FHe was charged with a number of
OL,20,Foffences, including the attempted
OL,21,Fmurder of persons unknown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
