FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FThe other offences are compelling a
OL,7,Fperson to use a vehicle for an
OL,8,Funlawful purpose; possessing
OL,9,Fexplosives with intent to endanger
OL,10,Flife or cause serious injury to
OL,11,Fproperty; the possession of articles,
OL,12,Fnamely a SIM card and phone, for use
OL,13,Fin an act of terrorism; and causing an
OL,14,Fexplosion likely to endanger life or
OL,15,Fcause serious injury to property.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
