OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FOutlining a "truncated" version of the
OL,7,F"extensive" investigation, a detective
OL,8,Finspector told the court that a call
OL,9,Fwas made at 10.09pm on Saturday April
OL,10,F25 for a Chinese takeaway to be
OL,11,Fdelivered to the Summerhill Park area
OL,12,Fin Twinbrook.
OL,14,FIt's alleged when the delivery driver
OL,15,Farrived in the area at 10.43pm, he was
OL,16,Fthreatened by two males.
OL,18,FHe said that police believe the
OL,19,Fdelivery driver was threatened with a
OL,20,Fpistol.
OL,26,@nD@MOUnD@WO]oD@AOUoD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FOne of the males put a gas-canister-
OL,7,Ftype bomb in the back of his car and
OL,8,Fthe driver was told he had 30 minutes
OL,9,Fto get to Dunmurry police station
OL,10,Fbefore the bomb would go off.
OL,12,FWhen he arrived at the station a few
OL,13,Fminutes later, he raised the alarm,
OL,14,Fthe court heard.
OL,16,FThe police were evacuating buildings
OL,17,Fin the area when the bomb went off at
OL,18,F11.15pm and "could clearly have killed
OL,19,Fanybody within close proximity of that
OL,20,Fdevice".
OL,26,@zD@MOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FThe detective outlined evidence to the
OL,7,Fcourt that a #10 top-up was purchased
OL,8,Fthat Saturday afternoon at a Centra
OL,9,Fretail store on Beechmount Avenue for
OL,10,Fthe same number that rang the Chinese
OL,11,Frestaurant.
OL,13,FHe said the next transaction on the
OL,14,Fmachine was a #20 top-up of a Monzo
OL,15,Fbank account linked to Smyth.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FHe said police had also obtained CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage from the location and the male
OL,8,Fwho appears to carry out those
OL,9,Ftransactions ` who he said can be seen
OL,10,Fwearing a green hoodie with "Brazil"
OL,11,Fwritten on it ` was identified as
OL,12,FSmyth by two police officers.
OL,14,FThe detective also said that the
OL,15,Fapartment block Smyth lives in is
OL,16,F"essentially next door" to the Centra,
OL,17,Fand when searches of Smyth's apartment
OL,18,Fwas carried out on Tuesday, one of the
OL,19,Fitems seized a hoodie with the word
OL,20,F'Brazil' on it.
OL,26,@rD@]OUrD@dO]xD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FHe said the phone that had been topped
OL,7,Fup stayed in the area of Beechmount
OL,8,Funtil it was taken to Summerhill and
OL,9,Fthe call to the Chinese was made.
OL,11,FHe said the defendant's personal phone
OL,12,Fappeared to be off from 4pm and was
OL,13,Fturned back on again at 11.45pm,
OL,14,Fmaking it inactive during the time he
OL,15,Fsaid "you could suggest the
OL,16,Fpreparation of this terrorist attack"
OL,17,Ftook place.
OL,26,@wD@FOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
