CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FAsked further about this, the
OL,7,Fdetective said that shortly after
OL,8,FSmyth's personal phone was turned on,
OL,9,Fthere are "very quick searches for the
OL,10,Fincident".
OL,12,FPhoenix Law's Gavin Booth,
OL,13,Frepresenting Smyth, said there had
OL,14,Fbeen a "case of overcharging" and
OL,15,Fargued that all charges bar possession
OL,16,Fof a SIM should be thrown out.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@IO]vD@HOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
