OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FHe said the "height of what they could
OL,7,Fsay is Mr Smyth is (alleged to have)
OL,8,Fbought top-up for a phone" and said
OL,9,Fhis activities appeared to be "the
OL,10,Fnormal conduct" of a person on a
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,F"If somebody was a committed terrorist
OL,14,F(as the prosecution are claiming Mr
OL,15,FSmyth to be), I don't think he'd go
OL,16,Finto a shop with CCTV and buy a top-
OL,17,Fup," he told the court.
OL,26,@nD@MOUpD@ZO]qD@_OUrD@OO]uD@AOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
