CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777911069
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FHe said that the incident was "pretty
OL,7,Fwell-known" and "all over the news" by
OL,8,Fthe time the search for the incident
OL,9,Fwas made on Smyth's personal phone, to
OL,10,Fwhich the detective said he could not
OL,11,Fconfirm that as he was in bed at the
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FThe judge said she was satisfied there
OL,15,Fwas enough evidence to connect the
OL,16,Fdefendant to the charges, when taking
OL,17,F"all the strands together" and
OL,18,Fconsidering there may be further
OL,19,Fevidence at a later stage.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@KO]oD@QOUoD@cO]yD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
