OL,3,CMan appears in court charged over
OL,4,CDunmurry police station car bomb attack
OL,6,FThere was no application for bail and
OL,7,Fan application for legal aid was
OL,8,Fgranted.
OL,10,FSmyth is due to appear via videolink
OL,11,Fat Lisburn Magistrates' Court on May
OL,12,F18.
